Title: 调用关系图
Describe: S06_CALL_RELATIONSHIPS。展示跨包边界的调用链，避免只重复局部对象职责。
------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
从用户 API 到 provider SDK

[Description]
典型 chat model 调用从用户代码进入 Runnable 接口，经 BaseChatModel 生命周期包装后，到 partner 包和 provider SDK。

[UML]
@startuml
participant "应用代码" as App
participant "langchain v1\ncreate_agent" as Agent
participant "langchain_core\nRunnable" as Runnable
participant "langchain_core\nBaseChatModel" as CoreModel
participant "langchain_openai\nChatOpenAI" as ChatOpenAI
participant "openai SDK" as OpenAISDK

App -> Agent: invoke agent
Agent -> Runnable: invoke graph node
Runnable -> CoreModel: invoke messages
CoreModel -> ChatOpenAI: provider _generate/_stream
ChatOpenAI -> OpenAISDK: HTTP API request
OpenAISDK --> ChatOpenAI: provider response
ChatOpenAI --> CoreModel: ChatResult
CoreModel --> Runnable: AIMessage
Runnable --> Agent: updated state
Agent --> App: final response
@enduml

[Detail]
调用方向跨越 v1、Core、partner 和外部 SDK。`ChatOpenAI` 的源码位于 `libs/partners/openai/langchain_openai/chat_models/base.py:2534`，文件顶部明确警告它只面向官方 OpenAI API 规范，非标准 OpenAI-compatible provider 应使用 provider-specific 包。这是维护边界：不能为了 OpenRouter、vLLM 或 DeepSeek 的非标准字段随意扩展 OpenAI 包。

------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
工具调用链

[Description]
Tool 调用链从模型生成 `tool_calls` 开始，经 LangGraph `ToolNode` 找到注册 `BaseTool`，再把结果回写为 `ToolMessage`。

[UML]
@startuml
participant "AIMessage" as AI
participant "ToolNode" as ToolNode
participant "BaseTool" as BaseTool
participant "用户函数" as UserFunc
participant "state.messages" as Messages

AI -> ToolNode: tool_calls
ToolNode -> BaseTool: invoke tool input
BaseTool -> UserFunc: 调用同步或异步函数
UserFunc --> BaseTool: 原始结果
BaseTool --> ToolNode: tool output
ToolNode -> Messages: 追加 ToolMessage
@enduml

[Detail]
`BaseTool` 位于 `libs/core/langchain_core/tools/base.py:405`，它继承 `RunnableSerializable`，所以工具也是可组合运行单元。工具 schema 由函数签名、Pydantic schema、Annotated 描述和 Google-style docstring 共同推断。边界风险在于 tool input schema 和模型产生的 tool call 参数必须一致，否则会在 tool 执行前后产生验证错误。

